        schema:description "Threatened species as published by a Declaration under s178, s181, and s183 of the Environment Protection and Biodiversity Conservation Act 1999. Plant names are identified using APNI name IRIs where available. Animal taxa are identified using Australian Faunal Directory taxon concept IRIs, generated by reconciling EPBC names against AFD and adding high-confidence one-to-one matches." ;
